description: Sunwell 5EC contains Quizalofop-p-ethyl, a selective herbicide effective against grass weeds in jute cultivation. It specifically targets grass weeds like Soto sheyama and Anguli ghash while being safe for jute crops. The product provides excellent selectivity and crop safety.
side_effect: May cause mild skin irritation. Avoid contact with eyes. Use protective clothing during application. Do not apply to other crops as it may cause damage.
crops_pests: Jute weeds e.g. Soto sheyama, Anguli ghash etc.
symptoms: Weed infestation causing competition for nutrients, water, and sunlight, leading to reduced crop yield and quality
causes: Grass weeds competing with jute crops for resources
